BETTER HOMES AND GARDENS HOPE REALTY

data.description: Not too remote, not too crowded, this 1200 square foot freshly updated home is “JUST RIGHT”! Located on the outskirts of the logging river town of Priest River between Newport and Sandpoint, this clean 2 bedroom 1 bathroom house is situated on a good size 0.19 acre lot and is move-in ready. A 3rd bedroom can be installed in the extra large living room space if preferred. It comes freshly painted with new flooring, light fixtures, and even a new hot water heater for peace of mind. The single car attached garage makes coming home with groceries a pleasure. The town boat launch and state park with sandy beach is a couple minutes away. Get in the Pend Oreille River during the summer or enjoy the dog sled or snowmobile races at Priest Lake during the winter. Enjoy Idaho living in a great new home and community!
